prompts.frontCover:
A whimsical, dreamy fantasy anime-style illustration of a slightly grumpy but adorable cartoon capybara wearing a tiny, sparkling fairy princess crown that's tilted to one side. The capybara is lounging majestically in a magical, pastel-colored hot spring, surrounded by floating luminous lily pads and gently glowing fireflies. A tiny, cheerful bluebird is perched on the capybara's head, holding a single, glowing birthday candle in its beak. In the background, there are soft, fluffy clouds in shades of lavender and peach, with subtle, sparkling stardust scattered throughout. The overall atmosphere is enchanting, magical, and humorous.

Centered text in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script reads:
"Happy Birthday to my majestic, unbothered queen, Lao Lao"
